    "drops": { "xp": [100, 100], "gold": [0, 0], "items": [] },
    "lore": "Not a boss to be beaten. A spiritual adversary to be endured. He speaks the worst truths you already believe about yourself. He cannot be killed because he is not a creature — he is the Accuser (CCC 391-395). His attacks are questions, doubts, and twisted truths. Your defense is virtue. Your weapon is perseverance.",
