    "_design_note": "The most important fight in the game. You CANNOT win by attacking. Physical and holy damage barely scratch him. The only way to 'win' is to survive 8 turns while resisting his status effects through high virtue. Every attack has a dialogue line that hits harder than the damage. The Accusation is the cruelest — it uses YOUR gameplay choices against you. If you killed soldiers earlier, he names it. This is spiritual warfare."
